Markov TheBeast Install Instructions
------------------------------------

1. Compilation
--------------
Simply unpack the distribution file and call

$ ant

This will compile the sources and place them in the classes directory
under the directory you extracted the release file to.

2. Starting TheBeast
--------------------
To start theBeast shell call

$ bin/thebeast

To execute a script enter

$ bin/thebeast <filename>

It might be more convenient to place the bin directory in your system path.



